        <section id="device" class="sixth-section">
            <h1>Device & I/O Management</h1>
            <div class="main-area">
                <div class="main-area-left"></div>
                <div class="main-area-center">
                    <p>Computers use many devices: keyboard, mouse, display, USB, printer, Wi-Fi card, etc.</p>
                    <img src="img/device.png" alt="OS Device & I/O Management">
                    <h2>What this component does:</h2>
                    <ul class="no-margin">
                        <li>Controls input/output (I/O) devices</li>
                        <li>Uses device drivers to talk to hardware</li>
                        <li>Manages data transfer between devices and memory</li>
                        <li>Buffers data to avoid delays</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Example: </strong>A printer driver helps the OS translate your document into something the printer understands.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="main-area-right">
