            <div class="main-area">
                <div class="main-area-left"></div>
                <div class="main-area-center">
                    <p>The OS provides a way for users to interact with the computer.</p>
                    <img src="img/interface.png" alt="OS User Interface">
                    <h2>Types of interfaces:</h2>
                    <ul class="no-margin">
                        <li>GUI (Graphical User Interface): windows, icons, menus (Windows/macOS)</li>
                        <li>CLI (Command Line Interface): text commands (Terminal / Command Prompt)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>It makes the system usable and controls what users can do.</p>
                </div>
